183
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:09,550
Aren't you going back?

184
00:16:15,380 --> 00:16:17,350
I have decided

185
00:16:19,490 --> 00:16:20,900
that I will not leave

186
00:16:23,340 --> 00:16:26,750
