266
00:24:40,220 --> 00:24:43,070
Anda, don't forget to come sing with me.

267
00:24:43,260 --> 00:24:45,460
Hello Anda... Anda...

268
00:24:50,760 --> 00:24:51,950
P'Ryo

269
00:24:54,560 --> 00:25:00,350
will you sue P'Tee and me?

270
00:25:05,430 --> 00:25:08,710
